           </a>
         
            <a href="https://phys.org/news/2022-10-fluctuating-oxygen-animal-evolution.html" class="news-link selection-link">
                <article class="selection-article">
                        <figure class="selection-article__figure">
                                <img class="selection-article__image" data-src="https://scx1.b-cdn.net/csz/news/tmb/2022/how-fluctuating-oxygen.jpg" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAUEBAAAACwAAAAAAQABAAACAkQBADs=" alt="">                                <figcaption class="selection-article__description">
                                        <h5>How fluctuating oxygen levels may have accelerated animal evolution</h5>
                                        <div class="article__info">
                                                <div class="article__info-item">
                                                        <svg class="article__info-icon">
                                                                <use xlink:href="https://phys.b-cdn.net/tmpl/v6/img/svg/sprite.svg#icon_clock" x="0" y="0"></use>
